high_descs: Turn to the counter by the toaster.
Pick up the wine bottle next to the toaster.
Take the bottle of wine to the refrigerator.
Chill the bottle of wine in the fridge.
Put the chilled bottle in the cabinet on the left under the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled bottle of wine in the cabinet.

high_descs: Turn and face the toaster on the counter.
Pick up the bottle from the counter.
Turn around and stand in front of the fridge.
Put the bottle in the fridge and close the door and then open it and get the bottle back out and shut the door.
Go left and stand in front of the sink.
Put the bottle in the lower cabinet on the left below the sink and shut the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled bottle in the cabinet.

high_descs: Turn to the counter directly to your right.
Pick up the wine bottle on the counter, behind the lettuce.
Turn around and go to the fridge.
Chill the wine bottle in the fridge.
Turn around and go towards the sink, to your right.
Put the wine bottle in the left cabinet, beneath the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled wine bottle in the cabinet.
